# SVG Icon System

## Icon Categories & Sizes

| Category | Tailwind | Pixels | ViewBox | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Nav (L1 Sidebar) | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Sidebar navigation icons |
| L2 Submenu | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Submenu item icons |
| UI Actions | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Buttons, toolbars, utility |
| Product Illustration | `size-10` | 40×40 | `0 0 32 32` | Device/service cards (Card Machine, Sound Box) |
| Inline Small | `size-4` | 16×16 | `0 0 24 24` | Chevrons, copy buttons, status |
| Inline Medium | `size-5` | 20×20 | `0 0 24 24` | Status icons, search icon |
| Promo/Feature | `size-6`–`size-8` | 24–32 | `0 0 24 24` | Feature cards (Connect Plus) |

## Color Patterns

### 1. `currentColor` Inheritance (REQUIRED for all icons)
All SVG icons MUST use `currentColor` instead of hardcoded hex. The parent controls color via Tailwind `text-[color]`.

```tsx
// CORRECT
<path stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" />
<path fill="white" />  /* body fills only */

// WRONG
<path stroke="#004299" fill="#004299" />
<path stroke="#101010" fill="#101010" />
```

### 2. Duo-Tone Pattern (Product & Feature Icons)
- **Body shapes**: `fill="white"`
- **Detail strokes/fills**: `stroke="currentColor"` / `fill="currentColor"`
- **Resolved color**: `#101010` (Foreground) — inherited from parent
- Container does NOT set explicit `text-[color]`

### 3. Sidebar Icon Pattern
Same `#101010` foreground with `white` body fills. Size: `size-6`.

### 4. UI/Action Icons (Icons.tsx)
Simple outline icons: `stroke="currentColor"`, `strokeWidth="2"`, `fill="none"`. Accept `className` prop.

## Component Structure

```tsx
interface IconProps { className?: string; }

function MyIcon({ className = "size-6" }: IconProps) {
  return (
    <svg className={className} viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      <path d="..." stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" />
    </svg>
  );
}
```

### Product Icon (32×32 viewBox)
```tsx
function ProductIcon() {
  return (
    <svg className="size-10" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
      <path d="..." fill="white" />
      <path d="..." stroke="currentColor" />
      <path d="..." fill="currentColor" />
    </svg>
  );
}
```

## Icon Containers

| Context | Container Class |
|---|---|
| Device/service card | `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Promo card | `size-12 rounded-[12px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Circular (status) | `size-10 rounded-full bg-[#e3f6ec] flex items-center justify-center` |

## Icon Source Priority
1. **Figma SVG export** — product illustrations
2. **`Icons.tsx` library** (`/src/app/components/Icons.tsx`) — 90+ generic UI icons
3. **Lucide React** — supplementary only (`ChevronRight`, `X`, `Download`, etc.)
4. **Imported SVGs** (`/src/imports/`) — legacy Paytm brand icons

## Icon Colors by Semantic Meaning
| Meaning | Color |
|---|---|
| Default | `currentColor` (inherits `#101010`) |
| Primary action | `text-[#00b8f5]` |
| Success | `text-[#21c179]` |
| Warning | `text-[#ff9d00]` |
| Error | `text-[#fd5154]` |
| Muted | `text-[#7e7e7e]` |

## Rules

### DO
- Use `currentColor` for all stroke/fill (except `white` body fills)
- Use `viewBox` for scalability — never set fixed `width`/`height` in SVG attrs
- Size via Tailwind: `className="size-6"`
- Use `fill="none"` on root `<svg>`
- Add `strokeLinecap="round"`, `strokeLinejoin="round"`
- Wrap in bg container for card contexts

### DO NOT
- Hardcode hex in SVG paths
- Use `#00b8f5`, `#004299`, or `#101010` directly in SVGs
- Mix icon sizing conventions
- Use raster `<image>` inside SVGs
- Add `width`/`height` attrs to `<svg>` — use `className`
- Create icons < `size-5` for touch targets
- Use Lucide when matching icon exists in `Icons.tsx`
